This project is a small Firebase realtime quiz app for a confirmation party.

General rules:
- Keep implementations simple and readable
- Prefer vanilla JavaScript over abstractions
- Do not introduce React or frameworks
- Avoid overengineering
- Minimize file count and architectural complexity
- Prefer direct and explicit code over generic patterns
- Avoid unnecessary helper layers
- Use Firebase Realtime Database directly
- Keep UI logic straightforward
- Prioritize robustness and simplicity over scalability